[[Tidy]], also commonly known as [[HTML Tidy]], is a tool for correcting malformed [[HTML]] and/or applying uniform formatting to that [[HTML]].

The <tt>tidy</tt> [[command line]] tool is shipped as part of the standard [[Mac OS X]] distribution. Type <tt>man tidy</tt> at the [[Terminal]] for more information. 

